		<P>
			Founded by Ralph Nader in 1971, Public Citizen is the consumer's eyes and ears in Washington.  With the support of more than 150,000 people like you, we fight for safer drugs and medical devices, cleaner and safer energy sources, a cleaner environment,


 and a more open and democratic government.
		</P>
		<P>
			We stand up for you against thousands of special interest lobbyists in Washington -- well-heeled agents for drug companies, the automakers, big energy interests, and the like.  Our budget is small by comparison.  But Public Citizen is respected and eff


ective, precisely because we accept no government or corporate support.  <STRONG>We speak only for you.</STRONG>
		</P>
