			</A> is a powerful voice in the movement to decrease reliance on nuclear and fossil fuels and to promote safe, economical, and environmentally sound energy use through conservation and renewable sources.  Critical Mass prepares and disseminates reports


, lobbies Congress, and acts as a watchdog of key federal and state energy regulatory agencies.
		</P>
