<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Critical Mass Energy Project</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000ff" VLINK="#dd0000"
ALINK="#ff0000">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="/public_citizen/pclogo.gif" ALT="Public
Citizen"></CENTER></H1>
<P>
<H2>
<CENTER>
Welcome to the home page of Public Citizen's
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+3>C</FONT>RITICAL <FONT SIZE=+3>M</FONT>ASS <FONT
SIZE=+3>E</FONT>NERGY <FONT SIZE=+3>P</FONT>ROJECT
</CENTER>
</H2>

<CENTER>
<P><blink>
<A HREF="/orgs/public_citizen/CMEP/alert.html">Activist Alert! 
</A>
</blink>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/CMEP/eyes.gif"><A HREF="/CMEP/what'snew.html">What's New?</A>
<IMG SRC="/CMEP/eyesleft.gif">
</CENTER>
<p>

Please choose from the following for information about:
<P>

<center>
<TABLE>
