General Agreement on Tariffs and Trade (GATT) and the World 
Trade Organization (WTO) - <i>What you don't know may hurt 
you!</i></a> <hr>
<a
href="http://www.citizen.org/pctrade/vote/vhome.html">Public Citizen's
Global Trade Watch 1996 Trade Vote Index!</a><P>


<a href="http://www.citizen.org/gtw/resources/acronyms.html"><i>Learn the 
meanings of every trade acronym!</i></a><hr>  
<li><a href="http://www.citizen.org/pctrade/press/press.html">Global
Trade Watch Press Releases</a></li>
