<HEAD><TITLE>
Joining Public Citizen
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000ff" VLINK="#dd0000" 
ALINK="#ff0000"> 
<CENTER><IMG SRC="/public_citizen/pclogo.gif" ALT="Public Citizen"></CENTER>
<H1>
<CENTER>
Joining Public Citizen
</CENTER>
</H1>
<HR>
<P>
Your membership contribution of $25 will bring you a full year of
Public Citizen magazine.  For a gift of $35 or more, you'll also
receive the monthly Health Letter.  What's more, you'll be joining
a chorus of thousands who say Congress must work for all Americans,
not just the special interests, and big business must clean up its
act.  It's time for an end to business as usual.
</P>
<P>
To join Public Citizen, write to: 
<BR>
<BR>Public Citizen
<BR>Customer Service
<BR>1600 20th Street, NW  
<BR>Washington, D.C. 20009.  
</P>
<P>
Our internet address is <A 
HREF="mailto:public_citizen@citizen.org">public_citizen@citizen.org</A>, 
and our phone number is (202) 588-1000. </P>
