<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Radioactive Waste Policy</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000ff" VLINK="#dd0000"
ALINK="#ff0000">
<BODY>
<H3>
<CENTER>
<FONT SIZE=+2>R</FONT>ADIOACTIVE <FONT SIZE=+2>W</FONT>ASTE <FONT
SIZE=+2>P</FONT>OLICY
</CENTER>
</H3>
<p>

<CENTER>
<IMG WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=100 SRC="/CMEP/radwaste.gif">
</CENTER>


<P>
This year, the nuclear industry is lobbying Congress to force a
high-level nuclear waste dump upon the state of Nevada.  The
industry is backing legislation, that would slash environmental
standards, preempt state and local laws, and begin the largest
nuclear waste transportation project in history.
<P>
Public Citizen's Critical Mass Energy Project is part of a
coalition of citizens groups that oppose the industry's efforts.
<P>
Please choose from the following for:
<P>
<center>
<TABLE>
<TD WIDTH=33% VALIGN=TOP>
<UL>
<P>
<LI><A
HREF="/orgs/public_citizen/CMEP/radwastecurrent.html">Issue
Updates and Related Materials</A></LI>
<P>
<LI><A
HREF="/orgs/public_citizen/CMEP/radwastetestimony.html">Critical
Mass Congressional Testimony</A></LI>
<P>
</UL>
<TD WIDTH=33% VALIGN=TOP>
<UL>
<LI><A
HREF="/orgs/public_citizen/CMEP/radwastefactsheets.html">
Radioactive Waste Fact Sheets</A></LI>
