<DOCOLDNO>IA076-000512-B013-193</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.citizen.org:80/public_citizen/CMEP/pubs.html 198.4.52.38 19970210231009 text/html 11575
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
