<DOCHDR>
http://www.citizen.org:80/orgs/public_citizen/CMEP/otherinternetresources.html 198.4.52.38 19970210231154 text/html 6363
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Mon, 10 Feb 1997 23:13:18 GMT
