<h1><center>Power for the People</h1>
</center>
<center><b><p>

SUMMARY<p>
<i>
A Public Interest Blueprint for Electricity
Restructuring</i></b><p>

</center>
<p>
To order the entire blueprint call (202) 588-1000 and ask for the 
publications department. <p>

<p>

<center>Released nationally by<p>

Citizen Action<br>

Environmental Action<br>

Public Citizen<br>

U.S. Public Interest Research Group<p>

__________<p>

Released locally by<p>

Campaign for a Prosperous Georgia<br>

California Public Interest Research Group<br>

Colorado Public Interest Research Group<br>

Energy Cents Coalition<br>

Iowa Citizen Action Network / Iowa SEED Coalition<br>

Massachusetts Public Interest Research Group<br>

Nuclear Energy Information Service<br>

Public Citizen / Texas<br>

<p>

<b>July 3, 1996</b><p>
<b>SECOND EDITION</b>

</center>
<p>

_________________________________________________________________
_____<p>

Contents:<p>

<p>

Introduction<p>

Principles and Summary<p>

