<DOCNO>WT22-B36-109</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA077-000522-B010-238</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.citizen.org:80/orgs/public_citizen/CMEP/pubs.html 198.4.52.38 19970211001614 text/html 11575
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 11 Feb 1997 00:16:57 GMT
