<DOCNO>WT22-B36-124</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA077-000522-B013-84</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.citizen.org:80/orgs/public_citizen/CMEP/transportation/cartalk.html 198.4.52.38 19970211002435 text/html 155546
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 11 Feb 1997 00:25:13 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Content-type: text/html
