<H3>Getting started ...</H3>
<P>Information resources for <A HREF="HEC/HecResour.html">historical</A> and
<A HREF="LAW/legalres.html">legal</A> research, and for
<A HREF="http://www.iue.it/LIB/ext-eco1.html">economists</A> and
<A HREF="SPS/Inet/Welcome.html">social and political scientists</A> on the
Internet.
<BR><A HREF="search.html">Searching the Internet</A>, and an
<A HREF="http://www.iue.it/tools+things/AAiue.html">archie</A> search
interface.
<BR>Computing <A HREF="CDC/Welcome.html">documentation</A>.<BR>And other
WWW servers, located in
<A HREF="http://www.cilea.it/WWW-map/Cities/Firenze.html">Florence</A>.</P> 
</CENTER>
