<TITLE>Grants and scholarships at the EUI </TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" TEXT="#000000">
<IMG
ALIGN="left" SRC="http://www.iue.it/iue.gif" ALT="European Univerity Institute logo" HEIGHT="116" WIDTH="110">
   
<H1>Postgraduate grants and postdoctoral fellowships at the European University
Institute,
<BR> Florence, Italy</H1>
<HR>
<H2>Postgraduate grants: Admission, grants, application procedure, and
practical information -<BR>closing date for applications (postal date): 31
January 1997!</H2> 
<P>The Institute provides doctorate programmes in the area of the Social and 
Human Sciences.  Information about these is provided by the Institute's
<A HREF="http://www.iue.it/Servac/acserhp.htm">Academic service</A>.</P>
<UL><LI><A HREF="admiproc.htm">Admission, Studies and the Doctorate</A>
</LI>
<LI><A HREF="admictee.htm">Admissions Committee</A> 
</LI>
<LI><A HREF="grants.htm">Grants</A> 
</LI>
<LI><A HREF="authorit.htm">Grant-awarding Authority Addresses</A>
</LI>
<LI><A HREF="applproc.htm">Application Procedure and Forms</A>
</LI>
<LI><A HREF="accommo.htm">Accommodation and Practical Information</A> on
Florence and the EUI
</LI>
</UL>
<H2>Postdoctoral fellowships </H2>
<P>The Institute invites <A HREF="http://www.iue.it/JMF/Welcome.html">Jean
Monnet Fellows</A> and <A HREF="http://www.iue.it/EF/proj97.html">European
Forum Fellows</A> to participate in its research programme for up to a year.</P>
<H2>Insurance and health information for postgraduate researchers and for
postdoctoral fellows</H2>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="insuranc.htm">Insurance, Accident and Health</A></LI>
</UL>
<HR>
<ADDRESS>
E-mail: <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@www.iue.it">webmaster@www.iue.it</A>, 20 Aug 1996
</ADDRESS>
<HR>
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.iue.it/Welcome.html">European University Institute</A> 
