<HEAD>
<TITLE>Newsletters</TITLE>  
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<P>
<IMG
ALIGN="left" SRC="http://www.iue.it/iue.gif" ALT="European University Institute logo" HEIGHT="116" WIDTH="110">
</P>
<CENTER><H1>Newsletters</H1></CENTER>
<HR>
<P>
Within the framework of the <A HREF="http://www.iue.it/RSC/Welcome.html">Robert
Schuman Centre</A>, the Working Group on Environmental Studies provides an
interdisciplinary forum for the discussion of environmental topics among EUI
researchers from all departments (Economics, Law, History, and Social and
Political Sciences) as well as Jean Monnet Fellows, faculty and external guests.
In addition to seminars, guest-lectures and conferences, in 1990 the WGES began
publishing the 
<A HREF="http://www.iue.it/WGES/Welcome.html">Working Group on Environmental
Studies Newsletter</A>.
</P>
<P>
The <A HREF="EEA/Welcome.html">European Economic Association Student
Newsletter</A> is published twice a year with the support of the European
University Instiute.
</P>
<HR>
<ADDRESS>
3 October 1996, webmaster, e-mail: <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@www.iue.it">webmaster@www.iue.it </A>
</ADDRESS>
<HR>
<P>
 <A HREF="http://www.iue.it/Welcome.html">European University Institute</A>
</P>
</BODY></HTML>
