<HEAD>
<TITLE>Department of History and Civilization - EUI, Florence
</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<H1><IMG ALIGN=middle SRC="../iue.gif">Department of History and Civilization
</H1>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#them">Teaching and research themes</A>
<OL>
<LI><A HREF="#t1">History of European expansion</A>
<LI><A HREF="#t2">Population, family and gender</A>
<LI><A HREF="#t3">History of culture (16th to 20th centuries)</A>
<LI><A HREF="#t4">The development of industrial societies and 
modern political regimes</A>
<LI><A HREF="#t5">History of European integration</A>
</OL>
<LI><A HREF="#faci">Facilities</A>
<LI><A HREF="#staf">Permanent teaching staff</A>
<LI><A HREF="resstud.html">Research students</A>
